Text.SourceString: I usually work from 10 to 2 taking patients, reviewing medical histories or doing inventory.. Charles runs the cash register most of the time.
Text.LocalizedString: I usually work from 10 to 2 taking patients, reviewing medical histories or doing inventory.. Charles runs the cash register most of the time.

Text.SourceString: My most favorite part of the job here is creating health care plans for my patients..
Text.LocalizedString: My most favorite part of the job here is creating health care plans for my patients..

Text.SourceString: I am used to being in high stress situations. I feel like thats when my knowledge and trainings really kick in..
Text.LocalizedString: I am used to being in high stress situations. I feel like thats when my knowledge and trainings really kick in..

Text.SourceString: It sounds horrible but the adrenaline rush is addictive.
Text.LocalizedString: It sounds horrible but the adrenaline rush is addictive.

Text.SourceString: Paying attention to what you eat is a great way to stay healthy in the long run. Prevention is worth more than a cure!
Text.LocalizedString: Paying attention to what you eat is a great way to stay healthy in the long run. Prevention is worth more than a cure!

Text.SourceString: Vegetables are great source of fiber and nutrients! Make sure to incorporate them in your diet.
Text.LocalizedString: Vegetables are great source of fiber and nutrients! Make sure to incorporate them in your diet.

Text.SourceString: It would make my job a whole lot easier! Ha ha ha
Text.LocalizedString: It would make my job a whole lot easier! Ha ha ha

Text.SourceString: Just holler at me whenever you have questions about medicine or health. I know people get nervous about moles or rash sometimes..
Text.LocalizedString: Just holler at me whenever you have questions about medicine or health. I know people get nervous about moles or rash sometimes..

Text.SourceString: Being in the sun is fine as long as you remember to re-apply your sunscreen
Text.LocalizedString: Being in the sun is fine as long as you remember to re-apply your sunscreen

Text.SourceString: I like playing pool. Its a great way to make new friends. Also, Id like to think that Im pretty good at it too..
Text.LocalizedString: I like playing pool. Its a great way to make new friends. Also, Id like to think that Im pretty good at it too..

Text.SourceString: Sometimes Im too lazy to change after my shift, so I just go around in my scrub..
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes Im too lazy to change after my shift, so I just go around in my scrub..

Text.SourceString: I notice that the islanders here love fishing. Its a good way to unwind.. It trains patience..
Text.LocalizedString: I notice that the islanders here love fishing. Its a good way to unwind.. It trains patience..

Text.SourceString: Playing chess is all about planning and strategy. Just like with health..
Text.LocalizedString: Playing chess is all about planning and strategy. Just like with health..

Text.SourceString: I dont work on Fridays, unless I have an appointment in advance, or if there is an emergency or something. The clinic is very quiet in general..
Text.LocalizedString: I dont work on Fridays, unless I have an appointment in advance, or if there is an emergency or something. The clinic is very quiet in general..

Text.SourceString: Hows your week been so far?
Text.LocalizedString: Hows your week been so far?

Text.SourceString: I think I might need to go to Sam tomorrow..
Text.LocalizedString: I think I might need to go to Sam tomorrow..

Text.SourceString: We sell medicine and vitamin at the clinic. They can immediately restore your health!
Text.LocalizedString: We sell medicine and vitamin at the clinic. They can immediately restore your health!

Text.SourceString: I get all my groceries at Sams. He uses local resources which I love. The only bad thing is that you cant really find off season items..
Text.LocalizedString: I get all my groceries at Sams. He uses local resources which I love. The only bad thing is that you cant really find off season items..

Text.SourceString: Im not a very good cook, but I try to eat home made meals when I can. They're better option for you..
Text.LocalizedString: Im not a very good cook, but I try to eat home made meals when I can. They're better option for you..

Text.SourceString: I still eat out quiet a bit thought! Ha ha ha.. Old habit die hard huh
Text.LocalizedString: I still eat out quiet a bit thought! Ha ha ha.. Old habit die hard huh

Text.SourceString: I get tatooes from all the places I was dispatched to. Amongst other more questionable things. Ha ha ha
Text.LocalizedString: I get tatooes from all the places I was dispatched to. Amongst other more questionable things. Ha ha ha

Text.SourceString: Ready for Monday Player?
Text.LocalizedString: Ready for Monday Player?

Text.SourceString: Oh Player? as in Player Player? Its nice to finally meet you! Im Yuri. Im one of the doctors here.. So, if you need any medical advice or a friend. Find me!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh Player? as in Player Player? Its nice to finally meet you! Im Yuri. Im one of the doctors here.. So, if you need any medical advice or a friend. Find me!

Text.SourceString: A1-1. Who used to run the clinic before you and Charles took over?
Text.LocalizedString: A1-1. Who used to run the clinic before you and Charles took over?

Text.SourceString: A1-1a. Charles was here first years before I moved in. He worked with <NPCName>Dr. Murphey</> and <NPCName>Dr. Chen</> for a bit. Those 2 were the OG. She...<NPCName>Dr. Chen</>, was a surgeon, I believe. They’re both retired now. There is a picture of them somewhere in the clinic. [image icon of the picture]
Text.LocalizedString: A1-1a. Charles was here first years before I moved in. He worked with <NPCName>Dr. Murphey</> and <NPCName>Dr. Chen</> for a bit. Those 2 were the OG. She...<NPCName>Dr. Chen</>, was a surgeon, I believe. They’re both retired now. There is a picture of them somewhere in the clinic. [image icon of the picture]

Text.SourceString: B1-1. How many tattoos do you have?
Text.LocalizedString: B1-1. How many tattoos do you have?

Text.SourceString: B1-1a. Not a lot. Some of my tattoos kind of mix with one another. What about you, <PlayerName>$player</>? Do you have any tattoos?
Text.LocalizedString: B1-1a. Not a lot. Some of my tattoos kind of mix with one another. What about you, <PlayerName>$player</>? Do you have any tattoos?

Text.SourceString: Oh! Very cool! You have to show me your tattoos sometimes. What is it of?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh! Very cool! You have to show me your tattoos sometimes. What is it of?

Text.SourceString: Ah, you’re one of those. Hah hah! One of those ‘my tattoos have deep meanings’ folks. Not that its a bad thing. Deep thinker...I’d like to call it.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, you’re one of those. Hah hah! One of those ‘my tattoos have deep meanings’ folks. Not that its a bad thing. Deep thinker...I’d like to call it.

Special.SourceString: B2-2. No, but maybe in the future. I've been wanting to get one... Just haven't found the design that I <Italic>like like</>... You know what I mean?
Special.LocalizedString: B2-2. No, but maybe in the future. I've been wanting to get one... Just haven't found the design that I <Italic>like like</>... You know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: Hah! Cheeky. Yeah, I think you have a massive back tattoo of a purple dinosaur doing ballet.
Text.LocalizedString: Hah! Cheeky. Yeah, I think you have a massive back tattoo of a purple dinosaur doing ballet.

Text.SourceString: C1-1. What’s with hating flowers?
Text.LocalizedString: C1-1. What’s with hating flowers?

Text.SourceString: C1-1a. Aahh… I don’t know. It just seems like a waste...you know? I can’t eat it. They’re useless to me. Besides, <NPCName>Charles</> is mad allergic. He wouldn’t stop sneezing if I bring them to the clinic. And I’m never home...so I can’t appreciate it at home...I can’t appreciate it at the clinic. I can’t eat it… I said that twice, didn’t I? Anyway, yeah!
Text.LocalizedString: C1-1a. Aahh… I don’t know. It just seems like a waste...you know? I can’t eat it. They’re useless to me. Besides, <NPCName>Charles</> is mad allergic. He wouldn’t stop sneezing if I bring them to the clinic. And I’m never home...so I can’t appreciate it at home...I can’t appreciate it at the clinic. I can’t eat it… I said that twice, didn’t I? Anyway, yeah!

Text.SourceString: D1-1. The museum opening was a doozy. It was only me who showed up...and <NPCName>Scott</>.
Text.LocalizedString: D1-1. The museum opening was a doozy. It was only me who showed up...and <NPCName>Scott</>.

Text.SourceString: D1-1a. Oh that! Yeah, I heard from <NPCName>Millie</>. <NPCName>Scott</> was pretty bumped that only one person showed up.
Text.LocalizedString: D1-1a. Oh that! Yeah, I heard from <NPCName>Millie</>. <NPCName>Scott</> was pretty bumped that only one person showed up.

Text.SourceString: D2-1a. I was preoccupied with...work. And honestly, the museum isn’t really my thing. Glad you made it, though. I’ll show up the next time.
Text.LocalizedString: D2-1a. I was preoccupied with...work. And honestly, the museum isn’t really my thing. Glad you made it, though. I’ll show up the next time.

Text.SourceString: D2-2a. Yeah. She’s running the museum and library. I’m glad that the museum is finally open. She’s so excited about it filling up with artifacts soon...all she’s talking about at home.
Text.LocalizedString: D2-2a. Yeah. She’s running the museum and library. I’m glad that the museum is finally open. She’s so excited about it filling up with artifacts soon...all she’s talking about at home.

Special.SourceString: D2-2. So, Millie is like...Scott’s boss or something?
Special.LocalizedString: D2-2. So, Millie is like...Scott’s boss or something?

Text.SourceString: E1-1. What’s the story behind your tattoos? Which one is your favorite?
Text.LocalizedString: E1-1. What’s the story behind your tattoos? Which one is your favorite?

Text.SourceString: E1-1a. There is one from an old friend...maybe a story for another day? [unlocks a question in heart 4 about this]
Text.LocalizedString: E1-1a. There is one from an old friend...maybe a story for another day? [unlocks a question in heart 4 about this]

Text.SourceString: E1-11. Your sleeve tattoo is really cool! Is that the one your friend tatted?
Text.LocalizedString: E1-11. Your sleeve tattoo is really cool! Is that the one your friend tatted?
